 What we're saying 





 
 
 
 
 


Reinsurance Solutions
As your reinsurer, we do not merely assume your risks – we help you manage them. Transfer your severity exposure to Gen Re on an Individual Risk or Treaty basis, or a combination of the two. We will deliver the best solutions to meet your business objectives.



