Meet Our Team
 
 


 
We have structured our business units to maximize our ability to efficiently work with
each client and each potential client. By empowering unit leaders to make more decisions
locally and in real time, clients will benefit more fully and immediately from our direct
business model.
We are eager to help you meet even your greatest challenges, and to help you navigate
the uncertainties of the future as you pursue your growth and development goals. Please
call upon any member of our team to learn more.”

Kara Raiguel, President & CEO, General Re Corporation


 
 
 



