Breadth of Experience
 


"I am an actuarial student and mainly focus on Long Term Care, but in my short time at Gen Re I have also already gotten experience with many different products, including Life and Medical Supplement insurance. Each day is filled with learning, and I look forward to what my future at Gen Re has in store."



