Careers @ Gen Re
A career at Gen Re means joining a global organization that delivers reinsurance and insurance solutions to companies in all segments of the industry. Gen Re, a Berkshire Hathaway company, is one of the leading reinsurers in the world, specializing in Property/Casualty and Life/Health reinsurance.
The insurance, reinsurance and investment management companies within General Re Corporation include: Gen Re Intermediaries, NEAM, General Star, Genesis, USAU and Faraday.
Unsolicited CVs are welcome and can be submitted to the right.  To see if we have an office near you, please view our global office locations.
The Gen Re Culture
Gen Re values excellence, integrity, personal responsibility, diversity and optimism. Our flat management structure and team-based environment promote collaboration and free-flowing communication. Gen Re employees enjoy a strong work/life balance, and a comprehensive benefits and compensation structure.
Gen Re fosters a culture of ongoing training and personal development. The company encourages employees to participate in in-house programs (such as business skills and leadership) and external technical seminars. We also reward employees for attaining industry certifications/qualifications. 
