Our Culture
 


"Having been at Gen Re for over a year now, I find that the knowledge I have gained through in-branch training and CPCU testing has grown exponentially in a short amount of time. We are constantly being challenged to learn more and do more to broaden our industry knowledge."



"Having been at Gen Re for over a year now, I find that the knowledge I have gained through in-branch training and CPCU testing has grown exponentially in a short amount of time. We are constantly being challenged to learn more and do more to broaden our industry knowledge."

 



